Okay, I promise.

503
00:37:30,150 --> 00:37:31,690
Stroke.

504
00:37:32,070 --> 00:37:34,920
Blockage in her hepatic vein, coughing blood,

505
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:36,860
trouble breathing, and Raynaud's.

506
00:37:36,860 --> 00:37:41,300
If we hadn't already ruled it out, it sounds like textbook pulmonary embolism.

507
00:37:41,300 --> 00:37:43,180
What mimics a clot but isn't a clot?

508
00:37:43,180 --> 00:37:45,650
Fungal infection. Her CSF was clean.

509
00:37:45,650 --> 00:37:48,660
No bacterial or fungal markers.
