00:39:51,740 --> 00:39:54,600
after you confessed your fear of dolphins.

533
00:39:58,520 --> 00:40:02,480
Can we just tone down the bromance a few notches? My leg is killing me.

534
00:40:03,290 --> 00:40:05,200
One last favor.

535
00:40:05,690 --> 00:40:10,330
I'd like to actually make it to the bathroom this time.

536
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:29,280
I thought you said you had plenty of Vicodin.

537
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:31,210
Everybody lies.

538
00:40:31,610 --> 00:40:34,350
So the way I felt, you feel that, what,

539
00:40:34,350 --> 00:40:36,140
most of the time?

540
00:40:37,040 --> 00:40:41,310
It really does suck being you, doesn't it? At least I don't have cancer.

541
00:40:56,090 --> 00:40:57,690
The tumor was benign.

542
00:40:57,690 --> 00:40:59,990
<i>And we were able to remove all of it.</i>

543
00:40:59,990 --> 00:41:02,530
Does this mean I'm not sick anymore?

544
00:41:05,290 --> 00:41:07,960
No, honey.

545
00:41:08,700 --> 00:41:10,620
<i>The tumor didn't cause</i>

546
00:41:10,620 --> 00:41:12,660
<i>your genetic condition.</i>

547
00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:15,470
You're still sick.

548
00:41:16,330 --> 00:41:18,980
<i>But we never let that stop us before, right?</i>

549
00:41:20,820 --> 00:41:23,300
So what do you want to do when we get out of here?

550
00:41:23,490 --> 00:41:24,940
Have you been to the aquarium?

